Package think.rpgitems.power.impl

Class PowerPumpkin

  • java.lang.Object
    • think.rpgitems.power.impl.BasePower
      • think.rpgitems.power.impl.PowerPumpkin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Power, PowerHit
    public class PowerPumpkin
extends BasePower
implements PowerHit
    Power pumpkin.

    When hit skeleton or zombie, will have a 1/chance chance to make them wear pumpkin head. And the pumpkin will have a chance of drop to drop when the mobs die.
